           <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n师资队伍</div>\n                <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">        \n                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资信息</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1/rngcyjs1/ALL.htm\">ALL</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"\">正文</a>\n</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"clearfix \">\n                             <ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\"><li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资信息</a></li>\n                    \n<li><a href=\"../../szdw/ltxjs.htm\">离退休教师</a></li>\n                    \n</ul>\n            </div>\n        </div> </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n                 <ul class=\"banner-ul pull-right tabs-ul clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\"></ul>\n        </div>\n      \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/jquery/jquery-latest.min.js\"></script>\n <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/E/C7/D7/1DEE5807238FBC1AC027CC96961_80D4757A_79F1.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>周托</a>副研究员</div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                        <p>办公电话：010-62799641</p>\n                        <p>电子邮箱：zhoutuo@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                        <p>通讯地址：北京市海淀区清华大学能源与动力工程系</p>\n                        <p>邮编：100084</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"sz\"><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"></div><div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: 700; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"></span></strong></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  教育背景&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;\n  <br> \n </div></h4>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">上海理工大学 热能工程专业 博士</p>\n<h4></h4>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  工作履历 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\n  <br> \n </div></h4>\n<p>2007.7-2008.10 西肯塔基大学访问学者</p>\n<p>2011.4-2019.9 中国科学院工程热物理研究所</p>\n<p>2019.9-至今 清华大学能源与动力工程系</p>\n<h4></h4>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  研究领域\n </div></h4>\n<p>碳基燃料清洁高效燃烧、工业流程的余热利用及污染物治理技术</p>\n<h4></h4>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  研究概况\n </div></h4>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p>\n<p>1、国家科技部，国家重点研发计划，660MW高效超超临界循环流化床炉内低排放技术研究，2016.7至2020.12，课题负责人；</p>\n<p>2、国家自然科学基金委员会，面上基金，循环流化床内铁酸钙催化还原烧结烟气中NO的机理研究，2023.1至2026.12，项目负责人；</p>\n<p>3、国家科技部，国家重点研发计划国际合作，适应可再生能源的发电系统灵活性规模化提升关键技术，2020.11至2022.11，子课题负责人；</p>\n<p>4、山西省科技厅，揭榜项目，智能化超低排放循环流化床锅炉与系统，2019.11至2022.11，技术负责人；</p>\n<p>5、山西省科技厅，重大攻关，面向新能源高比例消纳的灵活性低碳发电技术开发，2021.9至2024.9，参与；</p>\n<p>6、企业委托项目，烧结矿高温固体余热利用技术开发，2020.8至2025.8，项目负责人；</p>\n<p>7、企业委托项目，基础能源科技研究专项，2020.5至2024.12，参与；</p>\n<p>8、企业委托项目，超临界再热型双抽背压机组关键技术及工程应用，2020.10至2023.12，参与。</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"con\"><p>1、 中国电力企业联合会电力创新奖一等奖，2023年度</p>\n<p>2、 中国电力企业联合会电力创新奖一等奖，2024年度</p>\n<p>3、 冶金科学技术奖二等奖，2022年度</p>\n<p>4、 锅炉科学技术奖二等奖，2022年度</p>\n<p>5、 中国循环经济协会科学技术奖二等奖，2022年度</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"con\"><p><strong>论文：</strong></p>\n<p>1. Xiannan Hu, Tuo Zhou, Tong Wang, Rui Fang, Man Zhang, Qiang Song, Hairui Yang. Dynamic modeling and transient simulation of circulating fluidized bed boilers during variable loads. Chemical Engineering Journal, 2025, 506: 159754.</p>\n<p>2. Shuangming Zhang, Tuo Zhou, Chaoran Li, Man Zhang, Hairui Yang. Research progress and prospect of fluidized bed metallic ore roasting technology: A review. Fuel, 2024, 378: 132717.</p>\n<p>3. Tong Wang, Tuo Zhou, Chaoran Li, Man Zhang, Qiang Song, Hairui Yang. Biogas-to-methanol: A new green methanol production process based on anaerobic digestion of biomass. Energy Conversion and Management, 2024, 321:119065.</p>\n<p>4. Weiqin Lu, Zhihan Li, Xueyu Tang, Dinghe Liu, Xiwei Ke, Tuo Zhou. Simulation study on heat and masstransfer characteristics within tubular moving bed heat exchangers. Case Studies in Thermal Engineering, 2024, 61: 105008.</p>\n<p>5. Weiqin Lu, Changhao Ma, Dinghe Liu, Yanwei Zhao, Xiwei Ke, Tuo Zhou. A comprehensive heat transfer prediction model for tubular moving bed heat exchangers using CFD-DEM: Validation and sensitivity analysis. Applied Thermal Engineering, 2024, 247: 123072.</p>\n<p>6. Tuo Zhou, Zhiqiang Gong, Qinggang Lu. Experimental Study on Enhanced Control of NOx Emission 